Wanna know about a product that literally grows with your baby?? 
Say hello to @luvlap.in’s 6-in-1 baby high chair which can be used as a high chair, a booster seat, a table & chair for studying or playing, stool or just as a chair. Now that’s what I call it a multi functional product which allows endless options when it comes to your baby. Our lil baby Avo lovessss and adores this high chair and his most favourite part is to use the chair and table as his play area. 

It’s also very easy and quick to install as it requires no tools.
This also ensures maximum safety for your baby with it’s 5 point safety harness and Safety stop.
It has been made with an environment frinedly PP material & the seat cover washable. A true treat for your lil ones & super handy for the parents.

 #LuvLap #LuvLapIndia #LuvLapBaby #LuvLapHighChair #luvlapproducts #6in1highchair #MomBlogger #MommyBlogger #kidsofinstagram

Say hello to our newest and most dependable travel bud - “Urbane Baby Stroller” by @luvlap.in 
It’s the BEST travel stroller out there as it’s super light weight, easy to carry and move around with and it folds with just one click of a button. Easy and compact to store as well. As we explored #Phuket we carried baby Avo in this stroller from Malls to Beaches, hikes to long walks and in and around our villas. 
The stroller comes with 5 Point Safety Harness which means your lil one is safely tucked in there. You can also adjust the seating position or sleeping position as per your baby’s needs. It’s surely a spacious stroller with heavy duty wheels that make it an ideal choice for travels. - It has an extended Foldable Canopy, looking window in the canopy, adjustable leg support with extra wide footrest and a huge storage basket under the seat. 

Baby Avo’s most favourite part is their detachable hand rest, he loves to pretend play like he’s on a bike. Thank you #LuvLap for these precious fun moments!!♥️⭐️🧿

#SassyShifSays #MomBlogger #LuvLapMom #LuvLapIndia #LuvLapStroller #TravelStroller #luvlapproducts #LuvLapBaby #luvlapbabystroller #PhuketDiaries #Thailand #TravelBlogger

One of the most important thing that we as parents pack in every single trip, it has to be - “Diapers” & @luvlap.in’s Diaper Pants come with Aloe Vera which keeps my bubs rash free. As you can see during the entire trip, Avo baby was one super happy, chill & relaxed baby. And the diapers of-course had a huge role to play!! 
Baby’s skin is super sensitive & mamas, you need to take extra care to ensure their skin is not irritated or itchy. This allows them to sleep and play peacefully. 

#LuvLapDiapers ensures 12 hours protection for your lil one and the diapers are super soft. It has a 360 degree snug fit with a soft elasticated waist band. 
And the best part is that is that these diapers are available in so many different sizes.
